holiday set with her own gratitude in mind. The design is inspired by a nativity set her mom made when she was young. Brittany told us, \"My mother is my kindred spirit in so many ways and I can’t help but be grateful for her influence in my life. Conveying that gratitude was the perfect way to capture this message.”</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All our holiday sets come with a gratitude notepad and a fun mad lib you can fill out and share with a friend. We hope it helps you reflect on your gratitude and pay it forward. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"left\"} -->\n<h2 style=\"text-align:left\">Inside Eighteen B\'s Holiday Gift Sets</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our skincare gift sets each come with a two- or three-step regimen powered by b-silk™ protein, our proprietary key ingredient. B-silk™ protein is clinically shown to improve texture and smoothness for skin that looks firm, youthful, and healthy. With scientifically tested results, these sets make the perfect gift for skincare lovers and friends who deserve a little extra pampering. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a bonus, the packaging is so pretty you can skip the wrapping paper. Here\'s a peek inside.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"left\"} -->\n<h2 style=\"text-align:left\"><strong>The Bounty of B-silk™ Protein&nbsp;</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":590} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://blog.eighteenb.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/EighteenB-Product5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-590\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Indulge your best of friends with <strong>The Bounty of B-silk™ Protein</strong>. This set features the full Eighteen B regimen at a 40% savings, our most festive savings yet. Inside, you\'ll find our Firm + Replenish Serum (30ml), Hydrate + Restore Rich Cream (50ml), and Revitalizing Hydrogel Moisturizer (50ml). </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Designed with all skin types in mind, our multi-tasking&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.eighteenb.com/silk-facial-moisturizers/firm-replenish-serum\">Firm + Replenish Serum</a> replenishes skin’s barrier after cleansing and primes skin for moisturizer. The set comes with our two moisturizers – our lightweight <a href=\"https://www.eighteenb.com/silk-facial-moisturizers/revitalizing-hydrogel-moisturizer\">Revitalizing Hydrogel Moisturizer</a> and our deeply nourishing <a href=\"https://www.eighteenb.com/silk-facial-moisturizers/hydrate-restore-rich-cream\">Hydrate + Restore Rich Cream</a> – so you\'re covered day and night, hot and cold, under makeup and bare-faced. It\'s the best way to share the gift of healthy, radiant skin with the ones you love. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><s><strong>$275</strong></s><strong> $165&nbsp;/ 40% savings. <a href=\"https://www.eighteenb.com/holidaysets/\">Shop now.</a></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"left\"} -->\n<h2 style=\"text-align:left\"><strong>The Gift of R+R (Replenish + Restore)</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":589} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://blog.eighteenb.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/EighteenB-Product9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-589\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>An ideal hostess gift, <strong>The Gift of R+R (Replenish + Restore) </strong>includes our Firm + Replenish Serum (30ml) and our bestselling Hydrate + Restore Rich Cream (50ml). </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our nourishing cream moisturizer deeply hydrates to rejuvenate skin, reduce the appearance of fine lines, and