ct11-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-587\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>The Starter Set </strong>comes with our Revitalizing Hydrogel Moisturizer and Hydrate + Restore Rich Cream in 15ml size. A perfect stocking stuffer, The Starter Set comes with approximately four weeks of product in travel-sized packaging. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Consider it an introduction to the Eighteen B regimen, or a thoughtful gift for a frequent flyer who already loves Eighteen B. B-silk™ protein was clinically shown to improve skin’s appearance in just four weeks, so real results can be expected. Good things can come in small packages. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><s><strong>$54</strong></s><strong> $50 / 7% savings. <a href=\"https://www.eighteenb.com/holidaysets/\">Shop now.</a></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Do you have questions? Comments? Topics you want us to cover? We’d love to hear from you. Email us at thelab@eighteenb.com.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Eighteen B Holiday Gift Sets Are Here: A Peek Inside','Our holiday gift sets are finally here. In this post, we take a look inside each set. Here\'s what\'s inside, who it\'s right for, and why they make the perfect gift for skincare lovers.','publish','open','open','','eighteen-b-holiday-sets-are-here','','','2019-11-05 16:34:08','2019-11-05 16:34:08','',0,'https://blog.eighteenb.com/?p=575',0,'post','',0),(572,3,'2019-10-29 13:28:31','2019-10-29 13:28:31','','EighteenB-Women-Brittany-Jepsen-The-House-That-Lars-Built-3353','','inherit','open','closed','','eighteenb-women-brittany-jepsen-the-house-that-lars-built-3353','','','2019-10-29 13:28:31','2019-10-29 13:28:31','',561,'https://blog.eighteenb.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/EighteenB-Women-Brittany-Jepsen-The-House-That-Lars-Built-3353.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(573,3,'2019-10-29 13:31:41','2019-10-29 13:31:41','','Eight